<P>__{(she turns invitingly)}
<D>__{no why? should i?}
<C>__{baron}
<D>__{lord no charming but why one meal a day?}
<C>__{flaemmchen}
<P>__{(laughing in his face)}
<D>__{money ever heard of it?}
